@startuml
autonumber
title Security Evaluation Tool - Conceptual Populate DB Flow

actor User
participant "CLI" as CLI
participant "DocumentLoader"
participant "VectorStore"

User -> CLI: populate-db()
activate CLI
CLI -> DocumentLoader: load_and_split_docs()
activate DocumentLoader
DocumentLoader --> CLI: load_and_split_docs: chunks_with_metadata
deactivate DocumentLoader
CLI -> VectorStore: add_chunks(chunks_with_metadata)
activate VectorStore
VectorStore --> CLI: add_chunks: chunk_ids_list
deactivate VectorStore
CLI --> User: populate-db: None
deactivate CLI



@enduml
